
Data folder contains some txt files, it contain plain text data (it is not dictionary or json)
We must use string operation to extract data (for example, use split(":") to specify key-value)
The key is not in order, in p1.txt and p2.txt is name-phone-address-email, but in p3.txt is name-phone-email-address

Question:
    1. How many customers come from VietNam
    2. Print information of customer who comes from China
    3. Which is the most popular mailing service
    4. How many customers' emails in China